WEBVTT

00:02:59.863 --> 00:03:04.091
Sasa, kuna wabishi wanaoamini kua sanaa
inatakiwa kuwepo tu katika jumba la sanaa.

00:03:05.849 --> 00:03:09.615
Wanaamini kwamba haina matumizi halisia
zaidi ya thamani ya urembo wake.

00:03:09.639 --> 00:03:12.180
Najua ni kina nani katika kila umati
ambao nafundisha.

00:03:12.204 --> 00:03:14.949
Mikono yao wamekunja, miguu yao wamekunja,

00:03:14.973 --> 00:03:16.625
lugha ya miili yao inasema,

00:03:16.649 --> 00:03:19.222
"Nitajifunza nini kwa huyu mwanamke
anayeongea haraka

00:03:19.246 --> 00:03:21.187
kuhusu michoro na sanaa?"

00:03:22.875 --> 00:03:25.471
Hivyo nafanyaje ili kufanya iendane nao?

00:03:27.078 --> 00:03:29.309
Nawaambia kuangalia hii sanaa,

00:03:29.333 --> 00:03:31.594
kama hii picha na Kumi Yamashita.